name: Against_time:\\dorimu_no_sekai
description:
<message>
>You can run away from almost everything in your life, except for some things.
>Time is one of these.
>But how is it even bad?
>What's the point in eternity?
>Time can be your reaper, or maybe your savior from a life of void.
>Reject eternal, embrace ethereal.
</message>
